---
import BlogPostLayout from '../../layouts/BlogPostLayout.astro';
import { Card, CardHeader, CardTitle, CardDescription, CardContent } from '../../components/ui/card';
import { Button } from '../../components/ui/button';
import { Badge } from '../../components/ui/badge';
import { getBlogPost } from '../../lib/blog-posts';

// Export frontmatter for auto-discovery
export const frontmatter = {
  title: 'Content Marketing That Converts',
  description: 'Proven strategies to turn readers into customers',
  author: 'Michael Rodriguez',
  date: '2025-01-22',
  topic: 'marketing' as const,
  tags: ['content', 'seo', 'conversion', 'strategy', 'growth'],
};

const post = getBlogPost('content-marketing-strategy')!;
---

<BlogPostLayout post={post}>
  <p class="text-lg">
    In today's digital landscape, content marketing isn't just about creating content—it's about creating the <em>right</em> content for the <em>right</em> audience at the <em>right</em> time. This comprehensive guide will walk you through building a data-driven content strategy that actually drives results.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">The Content Marketing Framework</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 my-8">
    <Card client:load>
      <CardHeader>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <CardTitle className="text-xl">Research & Planning</CardTitle>
        <CardDescription>Understand your audience and market</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <ul class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-2">
          <li>• Audience persona development</li>
          <li>• Competitor content analysis</li>
          <li>• Keyword research & SEO strategy</li>
          <li>• Content gap identification</li>
        </ul>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card client:load>
      <CardHeader>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <CardTitle className="text-xl">Creation & Distribution</CardTitle>
        <CardDescription>Produce and share quality content</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <ul class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-2">
          <li>• Multi-format content creation</li>
          <li>• Editorial calendar management</li>
          <li>• Cross-platform distribution</li>
          <li>• Influencer collaborations</li>
        </ul>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card client:load>
      <CardHeader>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <CardTitle className="text-xl">Measure & Optimize</CardTitle>
        <CardDescription>Track performance and iterate</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <ul class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-2">
          <li>• Analytics & KPI tracking</li>
          <li>• A/B testing content variations</li>
          <li>• ROI measurement</li>
          <li>• Continuous improvement cycles</li>
        </ul>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Content Types That Drive Results</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Educational Blog Posts</h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">
        In-depth guides and tutorials that solve specific problems for your target audience. These establish thought leadership and drive organic search traffic.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <Badge client:load variant="secondary">SEO-optimized</Badge>
        <Badge client:load variant="secondary">Evergreen</Badge>
        <Badge client:load variant="secondary">High-value</Badge>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-6">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Case Studies & Success Stories</h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">
        Real-world examples of how your product or service solved customer problems. Nothing builds trust like proven results.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <Badge client:load variant="secondary">Trust-building</Badge>
        <Badge client:load variant="secondary">Conversion-focused</Badge>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Interactive Content</h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">
        Quizzes, calculators, assessments, and interactive tools that engage users and collect valuable data about their needs.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <Badge client:load variant="secondary">High engagement</Badge>
        <Badge client:load variant="secondary">Lead generation</Badge>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 via-purple-500/10 to-blue-500/10 rounded-lg p-8 my-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The 80/20 Rule for Content Marketing</h2>
    <p class="text-lg mb-4">
      80% of your content should educate, inform, and entertain your audience without asking for anything in return. Only 20% should be promotional.
    </p>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">
      This ratio builds trust and positions your brand as a helpful resource, not just another company trying to sell something.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Measuring Content Marketing Success</h2>

  <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Top-of-Funnel Metrics</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">1.</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Organic Traffic:</strong>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground"> Sessions from search engines</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">2.</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Social Shares:</strong>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground"> Reach and engagement</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">3.</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Time on Page:</strong>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground"> Content quality indicator</span>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Bottom-of-Funnel Metrics</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">1.</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Lead Generation:</strong>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground"> Email signups, downloads</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">2.</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Conversion Rate:</strong>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground"> Visitors to customers</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">3.</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Customer Lifetime Value:</strong>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground"> Long-term revenue impact</span>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Action Plan: Your Next Steps</h2>

  <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-muted rounded-lg">
      <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-1">Audit Your Existing Content</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Identify what's working, what's not, and where the gaps are in your current content library.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-muted rounded-lg">
      <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-1">Define Your Content Pillars</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Choose 3-5 core topics that align with your business goals and audience needs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-muted rounded-lg">
      <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-1">Create a 90-Day Content Calendar</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Plan out your content mix across different formats and distribution channels.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-muted rounded-lg">
      <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">4</div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-1">Set Up Analytics & Tracking</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Implement proper tracking to measure performance against your KPIs from day one.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8">
    <Button client:load variant="default">Download Content Strategy Template</Button>
    <Button client:load variant="outline">View Case Studies</Button>
    <Button client:load variant="secondary">Join Our Newsletter</Button>
  </div>

</BlogPostLayout>
